# Docker

- Always use specific image tags, never :latest in production
- Multi-stage builds for Python: builder stage + slim runtime
- All secrets via environment variables, never baked into image
- HEALTHCHECK обязателен для сервисов с базой данных
- .dockerignore должен исключать: .env, __pycache__, .git, tests/
```

